 Daughter）这一角色，她请求父亲释放囚徒，而且对歌喉变得极佳的索尼诺有好感。至于杜邦兄弟也有加入丁丁一等行列，并一起险些被活活烧死。\r\n","name":"Tintin et le temple du solei","name_cn":"丁丁和太阳神庙","tags":[{"name":"丁丁历险记","count":10,"total_cont":0},{"name":"剧场版","count":10,"total_cont":0},{"name":"欧美","count":9,"total_cont":0},{"name":"比利时","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1969","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"法国","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"瑞士","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"童年","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"漫画改","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1969年12月","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画电影","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"漫改","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"-1970","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Eddie_Lateste","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Film","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"童年系","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Hergé","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"丁丁和太阳神庙"},{"key":"别名","value":[{"v":"Seven Crystal Balls and the Prisoners of the Sun"},{"v":"Tintin and the Temple of the Sun"},{"v":"丁丁历险记之太阳神庙"},{"v":"丁丁历险记之太阳神的囚徒"}]},{"key":"上映年度","value":"1969-12-13"},{"key":"片长","value":"77min"},{"key":"国家","value":"法国 / 比利时 / 瑞士"},{"key":"导演","value":"Eddie Lateste"},{"key":"话数","value":"1"},{"key":"imdb_id","value":"tt0065106"}],"rating":{"rank":0,"total":20,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":1,"5":0,"6":4,"7":10,"8":5,"9":0,"10":0},"score":6.9},"total_episodes":0,"collection":{"on_hold":3,"dropped":5,"wish":11,"collect":38,"doing":1},"id":116137,"eps":1,"meta_tags":["剧场版"],"volumes":0,"series":false,"locked":false,"nsfw":false,"type":2},{"date":"1969-12-10","platform":"剧场版","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/59/9b/132404_6k33S.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/59/9b/132404_6k33S.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/59/9b/132404_6k33S.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/59/9b/132404_6k33S.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/59/9b/132404_6k33S.jpg"},"summary":"　　它是一只红色鸟儿（Richard Bakalyan 配音），自由自在飞在蔚蓝青空之上，哼着小调的它没留神遭到猎枪攻击。这个倒霉的家伙似乎习以为常，它为观众放上唱片，伴随着轻快的曲调，讲述了作为一只鸟是一件多么不容易的事。比如在天空中首先会遭到猎枪袭击，落到地面后还面临着各种各样的诛杀。之后它又讲述了生物的进化史以及鸟类的分支发展的过程，而与人类之间的纷争自然不可忽略。它展示了鸟类在人类历史上所起的作用以及对人类文化的影响。有趣的故事，发人深省的意义…… \r\n　　本片荣获第42届奥斯卡金像奖最佳动画短片奖。","name":"It's Tough to Be a Bird","name_cn":"做一只鸟真不易","tags":[{"name":"短片","count":10,"total_cont":0},{"name":"奥斯卡","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"欧美","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1969","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"欢乐","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"恶搞","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"美国","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"剧场版","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"neta","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"中庸","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"迪士尼","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"cartoon","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Walt·Disney·production","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"篇幅太长","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"做一只鸟真不易"},{"key":"上映年度","value":"1969-12-10"},{"key":"片长","value":"21 分钟"},{"key":"语言","value":"英语"},{"key":"制片国家/地区","value":"美国"},{"key":"编剧","value":"泰 伯曼 (Ted Berman) / Ward Kimball"},{"key":"导演","value":"Ward Kimball"},{"key":"类型","value":"喜剧 / 动画 / 纪录片 / 短片 / 家庭"},{"key":"IMDb链接","value":"tt0064504"},{"key":"话数","value":"1"}],"rating":{"rank":0,"total":12,"count":{"1":0,"2":3,"3":0,"4":1,"5":0,"6":7,"7":1,"8":0,"9":0,"10":0},"score":4.9},"total_episodes":0,"collection":{"on_hold":0,"dropped":4,"wish":2,"collect":28,"doing":2},"id":132404,"eps":1,"meta_tags":["剧场版"],"volumes":0,"series":false,"locked":false,"nsfw":false,"type":2},{"date":"1969-12-07","platform":"TV","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/c4/47/53773_Hz822.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/c4/47/53773_Hz822.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/c4/47/53773_Hz822.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/c4/47/53773_Hz822.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/c4/47/53773_Hz822.jpg"},"summary":"富士見学園中等部に転校してきた主人公・鮎原こずえが、不良グループを率いてバレーボール部に